data.description: Short term rental is not currently prohibited. Completed in 2020, this ENERGY STAR CERTIFIED home has solar electric for affordable utilities with a heated pool overlooking forest service land. Single level, includes an executive office with French doors, a large media room with pool access, 2 bedrooms & 3 baths. The gourmet kitchen has a large stone topped island as a focal point. Gorgeous wood pattern plank tile is easy care. Solid wood doors throughout.  The main bedroom has a view window, large glass shower, private toilet room & dual vanities. Garage 3rd bay is RV garage & can hold up to 40' RV. ANOTHER RV pad, with sewer & 50 amp elec., is along left side of RV garage. Fruit trees+herb garden & enclosed dog run. Quiet, peaceful neighborhood just outside city limits HOA fee $525 annually. Short term rental is not currently restricted.
